  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Toss the eggplant and red peppers with olive oil, salt, and black pepper, and roast in the oven for 30 minutes.",
    "Allow the roasted vegetables to cool.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the chopped romaine lettuce, crushed toasted pita bread, roasted eggplant, and roasted red peppers.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the lemon juice and a pinch of salt.",
    "Pour the lemon juice mixture over the lettuce mixture and toss to combine.",
    "Stir in the piccalilli and sumac.",
    "Season with additional salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional sumac if desired."
